Cell["\<\
Solving systems of equations (Chapter 3) and determinants (Chapter 4) are \
covered quite well in Math 220/225/230, however orthogonality (Chapter 6) is \
not and is critically important in modern applications.  As such, I will not \
cover systems of equations and determinants in class.  You may need to use \
them moving forward so it is good to review basic properties.  We will cover \
Chapters 5 and 6 in the time remaining.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9064703771964006`*^9, 3.9064704883265257`*^9}, {
  3.906472724808317*^9, 
  3.9064727397187176`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"017d599a-51e2-491b-9217-\
6210cef6601a"]
}, Open  ]],

